I"b<p>A new paper has been published in IJGI:</p>

<p>Liu, L.; Zlatanova, S.	An Approach for Indoor Path Computation among Obstacles that Considers User Dimension. ISPRS Int. J. Geo-Inf. 2015, 4, 2821-2841.<br /></p>

<p>The paper addresses the following issues:</p>

<ul>
  <li>The accessibility of indoor spaces related to a user dimension that includes a person and her/his operated objects</li>
  <li>A method to avoid obstacles and compute indoor paths with respect to the user dimension.</li>
</ul>

